"This was an absolute fun and delicious beer.  You have to pour this beer aggressively to get the effect of the nitro pour.  It worked really well and looked like it was poured from a tap.  The """volcano""" effect settled into a sweet smelling odor of chocolate and roasted coffee.  The taste was as smooth as silk!  It tasted like a milkshake, at times it was hard to remember this was a beer.  The smooth silky flavors coat your mouth and leave a nice feeling and leaving you wanting more.  This is a very nice beer with a sweetness to it.  I suggest pairing this with a desert or after a meal as a desert.  It was really a quality beer."
